Author: 5FootArmrest
Text: I vent using an online diary (handwritten could work as well, but not secure). Maybe you can try that? I don't have anyone to talk to, so I like to use my diary whether I'm having a good or bad day, and it's nice to see patterns or improvement in myself when I look back at posts days/weeks later.  If you need someone to vent to, my PMs are open :D (and for anyone else too)
